✔ Why Kendo Window Is Better Than Notification Here
Kendo Notification

Good for:

success messages
warnings
temporary alerts

Not ideal for:

scrollable help
formatted content
large instructions
Kendo Window (Recommended)

Better for:

online help
documentation
videos/images
long instructions
resizable dialogs

This matches modern Telerik usage patterns.

✔ Optional Enhancement (Highly Recommended)

Instead of plain HTML files, you can later evolve into:

Razor Partial Views
Markdown help system
Database-driven help
Context-sensitive help

WITHOUT changing your popup architecture.

